import React, {useState} from 'react'

export default function Form() {

  const [formData,setFormData] = useState({
    username:'',
    email:'',
    password:'',
    confirmPassword:'',
    mobilePhone:''
  })


  return (
    <form>
        <input
            id = 'username'
            placeholder='Username'
            name='username'
        />
        <input 
            id='email'
            placeholder='Email'
            name='email'
            type={email}
        />
        <input 
            id='password'
            placeholder='password'
            name='email'
        />
        <input 
            id='confirmPassword'
            placeholder='Password'
            name='email'
        />

        

    </form>
  )
}
